Title: Comment on: Non-perturbative finite T broadening of the rho meson and
  dilepton emission in heavy ion-collisions (by J. Ruppert and T. Renk Phys.
  Rev. C71 (2005) 064903; nucl-th/0412047 Abstract: In this comment we point out several problems concerning kinematical
singularities which are encountered in the calculation of the dilepton rates in
{Ruppert:2004yg}. We also comment on the method introduced in {vanHees:2000bp}
and further used in refs. {Riek:2004kx,Renk:2006dt,Renk:2006ax,Ruppert:2004yg}
